wcgs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu72wcgs.jpg&h=4e7ea801&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hdRT928.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhdRT928.jpg&h=fe5ef654&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n@期望連仔幫手壓制fake news <br />\n@上連登要用多用腦！<br />\n預備大型商場不合作運動：<br />\n齋睇唔買，儲多d錢；人多自然塞<br />\n連儂牆戰線不能倒！修建連儂，有你有我<br />\n<br />\n<ins>考驗毅力與堅持</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">做更具價值嘅野</span><br />\n#離開同溫層，接觸各種人，理解佢地嘅想法，將不支持我們的人轉為支持我們！這是成功的方法！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抗爭/革命搞十年八載唔出奇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">衛城革命，生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</span><br />\n<em>每日任務：</em><br />\n1. 優先<span style=\"color: red;\">幫襯</span>良心商店<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">抵制</span>「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">免費港鐵</span>（注意安全）；二人同遊，一人免費；買平飛；長者八達通<br />\n4. 夜晚<span style=\"color: red;\">十點咆哮</span>！（改9點會少好多人）<br />\n5. <span style=\"color: red;\">健身+運動</span>，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: red;\">每日一post</span>，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88qcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=a600e0c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n7. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n8. 保持<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span>，分析能力level up，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冷處理fake news/ rumour</span></strong> 、五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n<em>每星期任務：</em><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">低消費</span>，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">做孝子救港</span>，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n<em>每月任務：</em><br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF轉美國<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會、陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾；Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.14"},{"pid":"0cee70bb7e3a08caafcb6c9558a8eb02b1199717","tid":1566992,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:06:55.000Z","msg":"一路講「你係咪打我」<br />\n一路係咁被人斬係咩玩法"},{"pid":"8bfc813e2dbc19776bb97b0181850c1f39f175f3","tid":1566992,"uid":59242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e045425d67f492e6655e9770750fd22feaa6d93e","tid":1566992,"uid":7760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70847868275ff0b5b42dbede17be253929aa6174","tid":1566992,"uid":59242,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T00:32:50.000Z","msg":"應該報狗話有黑衣人破壞公物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即刻派防暴狗衝"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:30:49.000Z","msg":"你岩岩訓醒呀? 仲覺得報警有用?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:17:40.000Z","msg":"乜料呀 扮藍絲呀"},{"pid":"c2bac62e14ec63447e510f95dcad80650969c432","tid":1566992,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:20:09.000Z","msg":"得一丁友又夜媽媽，一棍仆濕佢啦"},{"pid":"d9d5a5f369081c29fc49ca69efa27b6894d4d048","tid":1566992,"uid":200495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:21:20.000Z","msg":"打得好 <br />\n影影影 影完會流血？"},{"pid":"a328ee812872b1758b96c34c6bd30cabc8627fa0","tid":1566992,"uid":33721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:23:00.000Z","msg":"得罪講句 你真係好撚柒 上黎取暖?<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n企出黎對抗係要俾班藍絲知道我地唔會就咁服輸。<br />\n<br />\n原來就係做沙包比人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人一日仲係依D傻閪思想一日唔會羸"}]}